RELOAD: Reload a ranged weapon

Syntax: reload <weapon>
        reload <weapon> with <ammo>

DESCRIPTION:
  Loads ammunition into a ranged weapon. The weapon must be in your inventory
  or wielded. Ammo must also be in your inventory.

  If multiple ammo types are available, specify which to use with "with".
  E-clips are standard for most Coalition and modern energy weapons.

EXAMPLES:
  reload cp40 laser
  reload cp40 laser with e-clip

SEE ALSO: unload, eject, wield, weapons
